    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Adventurer's Armory pg. 5</em>, <em>Legacy of Fire Player's Guide pg. 23</em></p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\">Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 5 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 2 lbs.</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d3 (small), 1d4 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> x2; <strong>Range</strong> 50 ft.; <strong>Type</strong> B; <strong>Special</strong> -</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Ranged; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Thrown</p><h3 class=\"framing\">Description</h3><p>This curved, scooped-shaped, 2-foot-long wicker basket attaches to your wrist, allowing you to throw fist-sized stones at great speed merely by whipping your arm forward. Loading a sling glove is a free action that does not provoke an attack of opportunity so long as you have a free hand. You take -4 penalty when throwing a stone at an adjacent target and cannot use the weapon to attack creatures in your space.</p>",
